<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="527" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="26.[151,1436,150,357]" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,269,186,212]" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">Remarks:</emphasis>
Body length 250–270 µm. Several specimens from the present collection remind 
<taxonomicName authority="Bernini, 1975" authorityName="Bernini" authorityYear="1975" class="Arachnida" family="Oribatellidae" genus="Ophidiotrichus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oglasae">
<emphasis box="[1187,1308,186,213]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">O. oglasae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bernini, F." pageId="26" pageNumber="527" pagination="429 - 504" refId="ref20826" refString="Bernini, F. (1975) Notulae Oribatologicae XIII. La famiglia Oribatellidae (Acarida, Oribatei) nell'Arcipelago Toscano. (Studi sulla Riserva Naturale dell'Isola di Montecristo, X). Lavori della Societa Italiana di Biogeografia, Nuova Serie, 5, 429 - 504. https: // doi. org / 10.21426 / B 65110013" type="journal article" year="1975">
Bernini, 
<quantity box="[181,237,222,249]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0165" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" unit="in" value="1975.0">1975</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in its shape of the anterior lamella (large lateral tooth on cuspis, short and round incision between cusps, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bernini, F." box="[181,331,258,285]" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" pagination="429 - 504" refId="ref20826" refString="Bernini, F. (1975) Notulae Oribatologicae XIII. La famiglia Oribatellidae (Acarida, Oribatei) nell'Arcipelago Toscano. (Studi sulla Riserva Naturale dell'Isola di Montecristo, X). Lavori della Societa Italiana di Biogeografia, Nuova Serie, 5, 429 - 504. https: // doi. org / 10.21426 / B 65110013" type="journal article" year="1975">Bernini 1975</bibRefCitation>
), but the interlamellar setae are short which is characteristic for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Weigmann" authorityYear="2006" box="[1050,1149,259,285]" class="Arachnida" family="Oribatellidae" genus="Ophidiotrichus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tectus">
<emphasis box="[1050,1149,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">O. tectus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in contrast to long interlamellar setae in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bernini" authorityYear="1975" box="[423,544,294,321]" class="Arachnida" family="Oribatellidae" genus="Ophidiotrichus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oglasae">
<emphasis box="[423,544,294,321]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">O. oglasae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(and 
<taxonomicName authority="Bernini &amp; Avanzati, 1983" authorityName="Bernini &amp; Avanzati" authorityYear="1983" box="[608,1059,294,321]" class="Arachnida" family="Oribatellidae" genus="Ophidiotrichus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="corsicanus">
<emphasis box="[608,764,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">O. corsicanus</emphasis>
Bernini &amp; Avanzati, 1983
</taxonomicName>
) confirming the assignment to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Weigmann" authorityYear="2006" class="Arachnida" family="Oribatellidae" genus="Ophidiotrichus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="26" pageNumber="527" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tectus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="527">O. tectus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
